fields.title: Wagtail
fields.content: Elegant. Open source. Easy. Wagtail is the new Django CMS from Torchbox. Wagtail is powered by Django and released under the BSD License.

fields.title: Foundation
fields.content: The most advanced responsive front-end framework in the world. Responsive design gets a whole lot faster. It's now crazy fast for designers and engineers to code and learn too.

fields.title: Cookiecutter
fields.content: A command-line utility that creates projects from cookiecutters (project templates), e.g. creating a Python package project from a Python package project template.

fields.name: Can add home page content item
Can change home page content item
Can delete home page content item

fields.welcome_text:
Welcome to Wagtail Cutter Foundation

Firstly, make sure cookiecutter is installed: [Installation](http://cookiecutter.readthedocs.org/en/latest/installation.html)

Then run:

$ cookiecutter https://github.com/chrisdev/wagtail-cookiecutter-foundation.git
